cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY 

This paper focuses on imitation learning for autonomous driving using images as input, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories. The proposed navigation command and model architecture also involve machine learning techniques such as deep learning, which are relevant to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of segmentation and depth information, which are related to the systems and control (cs.SY) sub-category.
